Package: tessera
Title: Topology-Enhanced Similarity and Structure for Entity Regime Analysis
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("João", "Tonini", email = "jtonini@richmond.edu",
           role = c("aut", "cre"), comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-4730-3805"))
Description: Implements the TESSERA framework for detecting regime boundaries
    in complex systems using similarity network topology. Computes multi-measure
    entity similarity, constructs and analyzes networks, identifies community
    structure, and quantifies regime divergence. Applicable across ecology,
    manufacturing, and high-performance computing domains. Methods described
    in Tonini (2026) <doi:PENDING>.
